lead_paragraph: Former Bayern Munich boss Felix Magath has been appointed the head coach at Shandong Luneng, the Chinese Super League (CSL) club has announced.

headline.print_headline: Ex-Bayern Boss Magath Takes Charge at Shandong Luneng
headline.main: Ex-Bayern Boss Magath Takes Charge at Shandong Luneng
